"{\"correct\": \"no\", \"explanation\": \"The lmplot() function is a figure-level function and cannot be used directly with the map() method of a FacetGrid object. Instead, regplot() should be used for this purpose, or lmplot() should be called separately for each facet.\", \"patch\": \"6c6\\n< g.map(sns.lmplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n---\\n> g.map(sns.regplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n\"}"